v4: add Himalayas + The Muse (7 sources total)

API
- Himalayas: public JSON endpoint, ~100-200 remote-only jobs
- The Muse: paginated public API, pulls 3 pages for ~60 jobs
- Both feed through existing dedup pass

Frontend
